ction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed; margin: 0in .5in 10.0pt 0in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-language: FA;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"FA\" style=\"font-family: \'Vazir\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-bidi-language: FA;\">حضور پررنگی در شبکه&zwnj;های اجتماعی همچون <a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/\">ردیت </a>داشته باشد.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-align: right; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo2; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed; margin: 0in .5in 10.0pt 0in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-language: FA;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"FA\" style=\"font-family: \'Vazir\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-bidi-language: FA;\">دارای گروه توسعه&zwnj;دهنده&zwnj;ی با تجربه&zwnj;ای باشد.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-align: right; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo2; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed; margin: 0in .5in 10.0pt 0in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-language: FA;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"FA\" style=\"font-family: \'Vazir\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-bidi-language: FA;\">میزان استخراج و توکن&zwnj;سوزی آن دارایی معقول باشد.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCx